description: This HBell wrapping paper roll set is perfect for gift giving occasions throughout the year. With three festive patterns including gold polka dots, stars and stripes, you'll find the right wrap for any celebration. Each mini roll measures a generous 43cm wide by 3 meters long, providing plenty of wrap to neatly cover boxes, baskets and more. The gold and white color combinations add just the right touch of elegance. The lightweight paper smoothly wraps presents without tearing. Small enough to stash in a drawer yet yielding enough sheets to wrap multiple gifts, this versatile wrapping paper set is a thoughtful addition to your craft supplies all season long. Store neatly when not in use to maintain their crisp appearance through future holidays.
